{"_id":"63fe2a00-3d88-4954-95a1-e89754ef959b","type":"Item","name":"Gravitic 3: Mass Alteration","system":{"skill":"Gravitic","name":"Mass Alteration","rank":"3","type":"technique","speed":"fast","defense":"strength","Target":"Single","range":"Long","Duration":"Maintained","cost":"2","description":"You increase or decrease the mass of a creature or unattended object. This can be used to:\nIncrease or decrease the mass (and therefore weight) of an unattended object by a factor of up to your ranks.\nIncrease or decrease the attack speed of a weapon (though not faster than Fast, and a weapon increased to slower than Slow simply takes a bane to attacks).\nGrant a creature a Boon to all movement-related checks, a Bane to defend against effects that would forcibly move them, and Resistance to fall damage, or the opposite.","domain":"Natural Philosophy","costtype":"","category":"ability"}}
