{"_id":"ccf2afb7-a20e-4da4-b296-83c1f0f42134","type":"Item","name":"Gravitic 1: Gravitic Field","system":{"skill":"Gravitic","name":"Gravitic Field","rank":"1","type":"technique","speed":"medium","defense":"","Target":"Area/Other","range":"Long","Duration":"","cost":"1","description":"You increase or decrease the force of gravity a Close distance from a point you choose. If you decrease it, creatures in the area can move freely, leap great distances, lift very massive objects, and so on. If you increase it, all creatures in the area are Slowed, and the condition cannot be removed until they leave the area.","domain":"Natural Philosophy","costtype":"","category":"ability"}}
